  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0da2\u0dd3\u0db4\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0dba\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Biker collided with police jeep and rider in hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A very tense situation arose between the police and the public this afternoon (07) after a police jeep collided with a moving motorcycle and the rider was seriously injured and admitted to the Nuwara Eliya General Hospital.",
        "The accident took place today at around 4 pm on the Nuwara Eliya Kandy main road.",
        "The accident occurred when the police jeep entered the motorcycle which was driving towards Nuwara Eliya without checking the road and the police jeep collided with the motorcycle.",
        "A group of people gathered at the scene of the accident accused the police officers who were driving the police jeep of being on the ground and there were bottles of alcohol in the police jeep, and when they went to remove some bottles of alcohol from the police jeep, this uneasy situation arose between the two parties.",
        "Without reporting the accident by the police, the police jeep tried to take the badly damaged motorcycle in the police jeep.",
        "In the face of strong opposition from the public, the officials of Nuwara Eliya Police took steps to report the accident."
      ],
